{% set father = 'CertUnlpNgenBundle:ExternalIncident:Report/Twig/BaseReport/baseReport.'~txtOrHtml~'.twig' %}
{% extends father %}{% block problem %}

We would like to inform you that we have been notified that the <em>host</em>  {{incident.hostAddress}} is providing insecure <strong>Network Time Protocol</strong> (NTP) service by responding to <code>NTP readvar</code> commands.


{% endblock %}


{% block derivated_problem_content %}


<p class="lead">Problemas derivados</p>

The <em>host</em>  under your administration could be used to perform <a href="https://www.us-cert.gov/ncas/alerts/TA14-017A">amplification</a> attacks to third party's, like:

<ul>
<li>Denial of Service attacks (DOS, DDOS).</li>
</ul>

{% endblock %}


{% block verification_content %}


<p class="lead">How to verify the issue</p>

To manually verify if the service is vulnerable, use the following command:


<div class = "destacated">

<pre><code>ntpq -c readvar {{incident.hostAddress}}
</code></pre>

</div>


{% endblock %}


{% block recommendations_content %}


<p class="lead">Recommendations</p>

<a href="http://www.team-cymru.org/ReadingRoom/Templates/secure-ntp-template.html">Disable</a>
<code>NTP readvar</code> queries.

{% endblock %}
